{
  "page": "Terrax",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\">Terrax</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Jaenara_Belaerys_and_her_dragon_Terrax_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Jaenara Belaerys and her dragon Terrax by Jota Saraiva.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/78/Jaenara_Belaerys_and_her_dragon_Terrax_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg/350px-Jaenara_Belaerys_and_her_dragon_Terrax_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"246\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/78/Jaenara_Belaerys_and_her_dragon_Terrax_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg/525px-Jaenara_Belaerys_and_her_dragon_Terrax_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/78/Jaenara_Belaerys_and_her_dragon_Terrax_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg/700px-Jaenara_Belaerys_and_her_dragon_Terrax_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Terrax and <a href=\"/index.php/Jaenara_Belaerys\" title=\"Jaenara Belaerys\">Jaenara Belaerys</a>, by Jota Saraiva</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Owner</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Jaenara_Belaerys\" title=\"Jaenara Belaerys\">Jaenara Belaerys</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Species</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dragon\" title=\"Dragon\">Dragon</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Terrax</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon\" title=\"Dragon\">dragon</a> ridden by <a href=\"/index.php/Jaenara_Belaerys\" title=\"Jaenara Belaerys\">Jaenara Belaerys</a>, a noblewoman and <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonrider\" title=\"Dragonrider\">dragonrider</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/Valyria\" title=\"Valyria\">Valyria</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Terrax&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Jaenara flew Terrax further south into <a href=\"/index.php/Sothoryos\" title=\"Sothoryos\">Sothoryos</a> than anyone had ever gone before.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_sothoryos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_sothoryos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Behind_the_Scenes\">Behind the Scenes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Terrax&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Behind the Scenes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Terrax may be a reference by <a href=\"/index.php/George_R._R._Martin\" title=\"George R. R. Martin\">George R. R. Martin</a> to <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Terrax\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Terrax\">Terrax the Tamer</a>, an enemy of the <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fantastic_Four\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Fantastic Four\">Fantastic Four</a>. Martin grew up a fan of <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marvel_Comics\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Marvel Comics\">Marvel Comics</a>, including the Fantastic Four.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Terrax&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_sothoryos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_sothoryos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Beyond the Free Cities: Sothoryos.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/index.php/Not_A_Blog\" title=\"Not A Blog\">Not A Blog</a>: <a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://georgerrmartin.com/notablog/2018/11/16/farewell-to-a-marvel/\">Farewell to a Marvel</a>, November 16, 2018</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible uncollapsed navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:Dragons\" title=\"Template:Dragons\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/index.php?title=Template_talk:Dragons&amp;action=edit